EXPLORING ADDITIONAL SECURITY SERVICES

Config
  Allows you to assess, audit, and evaluate the configuraions of your resouces.

    Track configuration changes over time 
    Delivers configuraion history file to S3
    Notifications via Simple Notificaton Service (SNS) of every configuration change
    
  ex: Identify system level configuration changes within your EC2 instances. You can view network, software, and operating system (OS) configuraion changes, system-level updates, and more.
    
GuardDuty
  GuardDuty is an intelligent threat detection system that uncovers unauthorized behavior.
    
    It uses ML to find common patterns 
    Built-in detection for EC2, S3, and IAM.
    Reviews CloudTrail, VPC, Flow Logs, DNS logs.

  ex:
    Detect unusual API calls in your account. A anomaly detection feature evaluates all API requests in your account and identifies events that associated w/ common techiques used by attackers.

Inspector
  Inspector works w/ EC2 instances to uncover and report vulnerabilites.
    
    Agent installed on EC2 instance
    Reports
    Checks: 
      access from the internet, remote root login, vulnerable software versions, etc.

Artifact
  It offers on-demand access to AWS security and compliance reports
    
    Central repository 4 compliance reports from third-parth auditors
    Service Organization Controls (SOC) reports
    Payment Card Industry (PCI)
    
  ex: 
    You need to access AWS's certication for ISO compliance. Artifactts provides a central repo. 

Cognito
  Helps you control access to mobile and web apps.
  It provides authentication and authorization
  Helps you manage users
  Assists w/ users sign-up and sign-in
  
  ex: 
    Cognito provides functinality that allows your users to sign in to your application through social media accounts like Facebook and Google.



